{"tid":2306957,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港電台：轉發讉責涉暴漫畫被澳洲要求道歉，倒打一耙，蠻不講理，十分荒唐","createTime":"2020-11-30T23:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T23:38:31.000Z","uid":290404,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1ac5fb48e580d6a9ad39c81146a4748693ecb18b","tid":2306957,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T23:26:28.000Z","msg":"新華社發表時評，<strong>就外交部發言人在社交網絡轉發讉責澳洲軍人在阿富汗涉及暴行的漫畫，引致總理莫里森要求道歉，表示詫異。</strong><br />\n<br />\n時評認為，<strong>自己國家的軍人在別國作惡，卻不讓他人說，甚至要求對譴責冷酷罪行的人道歉，如此倒打一耙，蠻不講理，十分荒唐。</strong>荒唐之一在於<strong>轉述事實需要道歉</strong>。荒唐之二在於<strong>全世界都可以譴責澳洲暴行，但中方不行。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>較早前，澳洲發表軍事調查報告，指特種部隊2009至2013年期間，在阿富汗濫殺39名當地囚犯、農夫和平民。</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562863-20201201.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562863-20201201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xD8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=2b855c22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562863-20201201.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9c8c2192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562863-20201201.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"87c5d28db28a0a5aa9239adc553be84cc3076e13","tid":2306957,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T23:29:37.000Z","msg":"支那人在別國作惡，卻不讓他人說，甚至要求對譴責冷酷罪行的人道歉，如此倒打一耙，蠻不講理，十分荒唐。"},{"pid":"d03d8e35d7765f64858f23e0e19d6dc118fb9aed","tid":2306957,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T23:38:31.000Z","msg":"真，好似支那咁，直頭係自己國家屠殺自己平民然後再唔俾人講，唔俾人報，咁先係最「忠誠勇毅」"}]}